data.description: This is a lovely brick home with limestone accents built into the exterior of the home. It sits on a corner lot of Fair and Central. This story and a half has a lot of home packed into a compact 1620 square feet. Besides the one car garage it offers a separate utility room, a den, kitchen, living room, dining room, 2 bedrooms, bath, covered outdoor back patio, large fenced in back yard with chain link fence and mesh to provide privacy for yourself and any pets you might have. This property has been very well cared for and is move in ready. Seller is being transferred. While the attic is unfinished, it could easily be made into 1 or 2 bedrooms. Close to the hospital and the Great Darke County Fair puts this home in a very desired location.
